PEP 8

1. indentation - 4 spaces
2. characters limit per line - 79 char in comments max 72 char
3. in multilines math operators go at the beginning of new line
4. new class and new function with 2 blank lines around
5. methods inside class with 1 blank line around

6. each import in new line:
import math
import random
import os
NOT: import math, random, os
BUT: from datetime import datetime, timestamp

at first: import standard Python library
second: related third party library imports
at last: local imports

if there are many of them each group separated with single blank line

7. Names convention:
- files names --> small_letters_with_underlines
- class names --> PascalCase
- variables and functions --> same_as_files

